A format restoration project for Yu-Gi-Oh! built from philosophical first principles.

The core goal: return the game to its original design ecology — meaningful tribute economy, Normal Monsters as a legitimate backbone, power earned through real trade-offs rather than combo chains and power creep.

The practical mission: build something stable, honest, and inexpensive enough to hand to kids in the Philippines and similar communities who deserve something genuinely valuable rather than a product designed to extract money from them.

